{"tid":2158363,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"逾80年歷史石圍欄因楊明醉駕損毀 重造料需25萬元","createTime":"2020-08-15T16:14:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T10:12:44.000Z","uid":240362,"like":901,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"5eca7a832ca8fc29c2862f48b05e0b648c0fb278","tid":2158363,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T16:14:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200816/E6OZAE7EOZFVXBHEBLPLIUPDFU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200816%2FE6OZAE7EOZFVXBHEBLPLIUPDFU%2F&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9EL2INpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=a87c3730\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200816%2FE6OZAE7EOZFVXBHEBLPLIUPDFU%2F&h=4506e35b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200816/E6OZAE7EOZFVXBHEBLPLIUPDFU/</a><br />\n<br />\n無綫藝人楊明8月8日凌晨涉及醉酒駕駛，其平治私家車在馬己仙峽道鏟上路邊，令一段3米石圍欄損毀。「城西關注組」成員張朝敦一直研究香港石牆，他翻查政府憲報分析，估計受損石圍欄在30年代興建，至今逾80年歷史，「好彩有堅固石圍欄，先可以頂住楊生架車。」他認為，若當局有保留石塊，仍可修復舊貌。中科興業董事總經理潘焯鴻計算，若要重造3米石圍欄，料涉及25萬元，港府可向楊明索償。"},{"pid":"7263495bc33637f1e00182a73b04ce04d76ab290","tid":2158363,"uid":132587,"like":475,"dislike":2,"score":473,"citedBy":13,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T16:15:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0b8692f4b7e9dac051a5c2e44366f73c45897f0","tid":2158363,"uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"7263495bc33637f1e00182a73b04ce04d76ab290","tid":2158363,"uid":132587,"like":475,"dislike":2,"score":473,"citedBy":13,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T16:15:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T16:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/