8363,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T16:14:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200816/E6OZAE7EOZFVXBHEBLPLIUPDFU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200816%2FE6OZAE7EOZFVXBHEBLPLIUPDFU%2F&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9EL2INpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=a87c3730\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200816%2FE6OZAE7EOZFVXBHEBLPLIUPDFU%2F&h=4506e35b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200816/E6OZAE7EOZFVXBHEBLPLIUPDFU/</a><br />\n<br />\n無綫藝人楊明8月8日凌晨涉及醉酒駕駛，其平治私家車在馬己仙峽道鏟上路邊，令一段3米石圍欄損毀。「城西關注組」成員張朝敦一直研究香港石牆，他翻查政府憲報分析，估計受損石圍欄在30年代興建，至今逾80年歷史，「好彩有堅固石圍欄，先可以頂住楊生架車。」他認為，若當局有保留石塊，仍可修復舊貌。中科興業董事總經理潘焯鴻計算，若要重造3米石圍欄，料涉及25萬元，港府可向楊明索償。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T18:20:50.000Z","msg":"狗蓄社D錢可以用了"},{"pid":"8d64ad3bb40bc97f3539c89bd460e9a93dc7449d","tid":2158363,"uid":209773,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7263495bc33637f1e00182a73b04ce04d76ab290","tid":2158363,"uid":132587,"like":475,"dislike":2,"score":473,"citedBy":13,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T16:15:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T18:22:04.000Z","msg":"英國人救咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45e02436fc2da33c6cc4b74b4f1e59595213020","tid":2158363,"uid":34099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T18:36:02.000Z","msg":"林鄭係咪都應該去探望下呢樣死物<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22a278148e42351440bf00553c49303ac33011bb","tid":2158363,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T18:36:41.000Z","msg":"可惜咁都撞佢唔死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00652db7b30acdfc8bfe346631b108ac50c3994e","tid":2158363,"uid":129340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7263495bc33637f1e00182a73b04ce04d76ab290","tid":2158363,"uid":132587,"l